                    <h4>自定义开发模板</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="lr-cover-info">
                    <small>通过设置生成单表或多表的增删改查功能。</small>
                </div>
                <div class="lr-cover-button">
                    <a class="btn btn-default" id="lr_custmerCode">配置</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lr-cover-box">
                <div class="lr-cover-img">
                    <img class="lr-cover-img1" src="~/Content/images/codeGenerator/singletable0.png" />
                    <img class="lr-cover-img2" src="~/Content/images/codeGenerator/singletable1.png" />

                    <h4>快速开发模板</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="lr-cover-info">
                    <small>快速生成必要的类和页面。</small>
                </div>
                <div class="lr-cover-button">
                    <a class="btn btn-default" id="lr_fastCode">配置</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lr-cover-box">
                <div class="lr-cover-img">
                    <img class="lr-cover-img1" src="~/Content/images/codeGenerator/serviceCode0.png" />
